title: 332 - No Recompense!
description: Dan talks to Jesse Margolis, founder of Overheard LA about what else: Mike Crivello’s Camera World; It’s a wonderful world of cameras! We attempt to get into the heads of internet trolls, also featuring a bonus White Walker locker room pep talk. Featuring Dan Harmon, Jeff Bryan Davis, Spencer Crittenden, Rob Schrab and Jesse Margolis.
